Summary:	CeGCC offers cross-development to create Windows CE apps for ARM processors
Name:		cegcc
Version:	0.07
Release:	1
License:	open
Packager:	Danny Backx <dannybackx@users.sourceforge.net>
Group:		Development/Tools
Prefixes:	/usr/ppc
